      <t>This document advances the specification of RFC 2560 [RFC2560] towards the acquisition of any data relevant to determining a digital certificate's reliability; interoperability with [RFC2560] is maintained. Such data include a certificate's revocation status, it's validation status and ancillary information supporting these assertions.</t>
